<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wǒ hǎo xiàng yī zhǐ shòu shāng de xiǎo niǎo 迦南549</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ hǎo xiàng yī zhǐ shòu shāng de xiǎo niǎo, wú lì shān zhǎn chì bǎng;
 tíng luò zài shēn shēn de dī gǔ zhōng, gū dān yòu qī liáng.
 hū rán zhǔ zài ěr biān duì wǒ shuō, nǐ bù huì gū dān;
 zhǔ lè yì hé wǒ zǒu guò màn màn rén shēng lù, tóng zài yòu tóng zhù.
 shén yīng xǔ wǒ yǒng bù piē xià wǒ, zhòng xīn yòu jiàn dào liàng guāng;
 wǒ lì shí dé dào wú qióng de lì liàng, bù gǎi biàn yóu zi zhuāng.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>549</hymn_number>
</song>